nodes.text: Tobler Ceel was a Gungan male who served as the leader of the Gungan Grand Army and was the most experienced officer in its officer corps. He fought during the Battle of Naboo against the Trade Federation on his homeworld of Naboo in the year 32 BBY. He was also a close friend and a former brother-in-arms of Boss Rugor Nass. Ceel had purple and white skin, and yellow eyes.

Tobler Ceel first appeared in the early drafts of the script for Star Wars: Episode I The Phantom Menace, but did not make it into the film itself. The character first appeared in canon in the video game Star Wars: Force Collection.
